Module org.cumulus4j.keymanager.back.shared

	Shared classes to communicate between {{{../org.cumulus4j.keymanager/}key-manager}}
	(either embedded in app-client or in key-server) and {{{../org.cumulus4j.keymanager.back.webapp/}app-server}}.

	Since the communication is based on REST, most classes here are {{{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_Transfer_Object}DTOs}}
	(sub-classed from {{{../apidocs/index.html?org/cumulus4j/keymanager/back/shared/Message.html}Message}}) which are
	transferred via XML or JSON.

* Maven

	After adding the repositories documented on the {{{../download/index.html}Download}} page
	to your <<<pom.xml>>>, you can add the following dependency in order to use this module: 

+------------------------------------------+
<dependencies>
	...
	<dependency>
		<groupId>org.cumulus4j</groupId>
		<artifactId>org.cumulus4j.keymanager.back.shared</artifactId>
		<version>${project.version}</version>
	</dependency>
	...
</dependencies>
+------------------------------------------+

